# Tworzenie ImageDataGenerator do augmentacji danych
augment_gen = ImageDataGenerator(
    rotation_range=40,
    width_shift_range=0.2,
    height_shift_range=0.2,
    shear_range=0.2,
    zoom_range=0.2,
    horizontal_flip=True,
    fill_mode='nearest'
)
In[9]:
# Funkcja do augmentacji obrazw
def augment_images(image_paths, target_dir, augment_gen, target_count):
    current_count = len(image_paths)
    original_images = image_paths[:]
    
    while current_count < target_count:
        image_path = random.choice(original_images)
        img = load_img(image_path)
        x = img_to_array(img)
        x = np.expand_dims(x, axis=0)
        for batch in augment_gen.flow(x, batch_size=1):
            new_img = array_to_img(batch[0])
            new_img.save(os.path.join(target_dir, f'augmented_{current_count}.jpg'))
            current_count += 1
            break
In[10]:
# Iteracja przez foldery artystw
for artist in os.listdir(data_dir):
    artist_dir = os.path.join(data_dir, artist)
    if os.path.isdir(artist_dir):
        images = os.listdir(artist_dir)
        image_paths = [os.path.join(artist_dir, img) for img in images]
        
        # Podzia danych w proporcji 80:20
        train_images, val_images = train_test_split(image_paths, test_size=0.2, random_state=42)
        
        # Tworzenie folderw dla artystw w zbiorze treningowym i walidacyjnym
        os.makedirs(os.path.join(train_dir, artist), exist_ok=True)
        os.makedirs(os.path.join(val_dir, artist), exist_ok=True)
        
        # Przenoszenie obrazw do odpowiednich folderw
        for image in train_images:
            shutil.copy(image, os.path.join(train_dir, artist, os.path.basename(image)))
        for image in val_images:
            shutil.copy(image, os.path.join(val_dir, artist, os.path.basename(image)))
In[11]:
# Augmentacja zbioru treningowego
for artist in os.listdir(train_dir):
    artist_dir = os.path.join(train_dir, artist)
    if os.path.isdir(artist_dir):
        images = os.listdir(artist_dir)
        image_paths = [os.path.join(artist_dir, img) for img in images]
        
        # Jeli artysta ma mniej ni 250 obrazw, dodajemy augmentowane obrazy
        if len(images) < 250:
            augment_images(image_paths, artist_dir, augment_gen, 250)

In[16]:
# Budowanie bardziej zoonego modelu CNN
model = models.Sequential([
    layers.Conv2D(32, (3, 3), activation='relu', input_shape=(150, 150, 3)),
    layers.BatchNormalization(),
    layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    layers.Conv2D(64, (3, 3), activation='relu'),
    layers.BatchNormalization(),
    layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    layers.Conv2D(128, (3, 3), activation='relu'),
    layers.BatchNormalization(),
    layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    layers.Conv2D(256, (3, 3), activation='relu'),
    layers.BatchNormalization(),
    layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    layers.Flatten(),
    layers.Dense(512, activation='relu', kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(0.001)),
    layers.Dropout(0.5),
    layers.Dense(num_classes, activation='softmax')
])

# Obliczanie raportu klasyfikacji
report = classification_report(validation_labels, validation_preds, target_names=validation_generator.class_indices.keys(), output_dict=True)

# Przygotowanie danych do wykresu
classes = list(report.keys())[:-3]  # Wyklucza 'accuracy', 'macro avg', 'weighted avg'
precision = [report[class_]['precision'] for class_ in classes]
recall = [report[class_]['recall'] for class_ in classes]
f1_score = [report[class_]['f1-score'] for class_ in classes]

# Filtrowanie klas z zerowymi wartociami
non_zero_indices = [i for i, p in enumerate(precision) if p > 0 or recall[i] > 0 or f1_score[i] > 0]
filtered_classes = [classes[i] for i in non_zero_indices]
filtered_precision = [precision[i] for i in non_zero_indices]
filtered_recall = [recall[i] for i in non_zero_indices]
filtered_f1_score = [f1_score[i] for i in non_zero_indices]

x = np.arange(len(filtered_classes))  # Lokalizacja klas na osi X
width = 0.2  # Szeroko supkw

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(15, 8))

# Kolory dla wskanikw
color_precision = '#4682B4'  # Steel Blue
color_recall = '#87CEFA'  # Light Sky Blue
color_f1 = 'plum'  # Fioletowy

bars1 = ax.bar(x - width, filtered_precision, width, label='Precision', color=color_precision)
bars2 = ax.bar(x, filtered_recall, width, label='Recall', color=color_recall)
bars3 = ax.bar(x + width, filtered_f1_score, width, label='F1-score', color=color_f1)

# Dodanie etykiet
ax.set_xlabel('Klasy')
ax.set_ylabel('Wyniki')
ax.set_title('Metryki raportu klasyfikacji')
ax.set_xticks(x)
ax.set_xticklabels(filtered_classes, rotation=90)
ax.legend()

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

# Wykluczenie 'macro avg' i 'weighted avg'
filtered_report = {cls: metrics for cls, metrics in report.items() if isinstance(metrics, dict)}

# Filtrowanie klas z precyzj > 0
classes_with_precision = [cls for cls, metrics in filtered_report.items() if metrics['precision'] > 0]

# Ucinanie ostatnich dwch wartoci (zakadamy, e to 'macro avg' i 'weighted avg')
classes_with_precision = classes_with_precision[:-2]

# Mapowanie nazw klas na indeksy, upewniajc si, e 'macro avg' i 'weighted avg' s wykluczone
class_indices = {cls: idx for cls, idx in validation_generator.class_indices.items() if cls not in ['macro avg', 'weighted avg']}

# Upewnij si, e classes_with_precision s w class_indices
y_indices = [class_indices[cls] for cls in classes_with_precision if cls in class_indices]

# Obliczenie macierzy pomyek tylko dla odpowiednich klas
cm = confusion_matrix(validation_labels, validation_preds, labels=y_indices)

# Wizualizacja macierzy pomyek
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))
sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Blues', 
            xticklabels=classes_with_precision,
            yticklabels=classes_with_precision)
plt.xlabel('Etykieta prognozowana')
plt.ylabel('Etykieta prawdziwa')
plt.title('Macierz pomyek')
plt.show()

report = classification_report(validation_labels, validation_preds, target_names=validation_generator.class_indices.keys(), output_dict=True, zero_division=0)

# Wykluczenie 'macro avg' i 'weighted avg' z raportu
filtered_report = {cls: metrics for cls, metrics in report.items() if isinstance(metrics, dict)}

# Filtrowanie klas z precyzj > 0
classes_with_precision = [cls for cls, metrics in filtered_report.items() if metrics['precision'] > 0]

# Ucinanie ostatnich dwch wartoci (zakadamy, e to 'macro avg' i 'weighted avg')
classes_with_precision = classes_with_precision[:-2]

# Mapowanie nazw klas na indeksy, upewniajc si, e 'macro avg' i 'weighted avg' s wykluczone
class_indices = {cls: idx for cls, idx in validation_generator.class_indices.items() if cls not in ['macro avg', 'weighted avg']}

# Upewnij si, e classes_with_precision s w class_indices
y_indices = [class_indices[cls] for cls in classes_with_precision if cls in class_indices]

# Obliczenie macierzy pomyek tylko dla istotnych klas
cm = confusion_matrix(validation_labels, validation_preds, labels=y_indices)

                 xticklabels=classes_with_precision,

                 cbar=True,
                 annot_kws={"size": 10, "weight": 'bold'},
                 linewidths=0.5,
                 linecolor='gray')

# Dostosowanie etykiet na osi X, aby byy wyrwnane centralnie

# Dodanie etykiet i tytuu
